song.title: Hypocritical, innit?
song.info:
--------------------------------- Oh gross! This is such a hypocritical song! The worst of it is that it's inspired by my girlfriend who is working in London as an au-pair. I think I miss her too much. This is getting too worse... One cliche after another...
PoZoR, 5-4-97
Oh? Some greets? Well, okay... All persons inside this party place (another cliche!) and of course Sjaak, Lenz, HQN, TCM, Ruuw, TBL, LED, Simba3.001, Lancelot and all Cheese Membaz. ---------------------------------
